  ReciprocalRankFusion:  K=60; contentKey from content_hash or truncated content; fuse ranked lists, RRF score sum 1/(K+rank+1); output with rrf_score in metadata.
  HybridRetrievalService: Parallel retrieval via ExecutorService (virtual threads) + CompletableFuture; scope CODE skips log retrievers; fuse(vectorCode, vectorLog, bm25Code, bm25Log, graphDocs); topCandidates = fused limit topK*2; rerank with original_source in metadata; resolveSource(metadata); timer flowforge.retrieval.hybrid.latency.

